    <title>OI</title>
    <url>/2017/06/25/OI/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="所谓讲义"><a href="#所谓讲义" class="headerlink" title="所谓讲义"></a>所谓讲义</h4><p>一些没怎么更新的东西。</p>
<ol start="0">
<li><a href="/2021/09/20/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E9%9B%B6%E3%80%91%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BA/">方法论</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/03/09/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E4%B8%80%E3%80%91%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/">数据结构</a></li>
<li><a href="2021/03/20/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%91%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BA/">图论</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/04/26/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E4%B8%89%E3%80%91%E6%95%B0%E8%AE%BA/">数论</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/05/22/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%91%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2/">字符串</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/06/17/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E4%BA%94%E3%80%91%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92/">动态规划</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/06/22/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E5%85%AD%E3%80%91%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/">线性代数</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/08/02/%E3%80%90%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%C2%B7%E4%B8%83%E3%80%91%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0/">组合计数</a></li>
</ol>
<h4 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h4><p>应当已经不重要的题解。</p>
<ol>
<li><a href="/2021/05/05/%E9%9B%86%E8%AE%AD%E9%98%9F%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-2020/">集训队作业 2020</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/06/10/%E5%8E%86%E5%B1%8A%E8%81%94%E8%B5%9B%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3/">历届联赛题解</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/09/13/ICPC-%E6%9D%82%E9%A2%98%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88/">ICPC 杂题浏览</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/09/01/2021-%E8%81%94%E8%B5%9B%E8%BF%9E%E6%B5%8B/">2021 联赛连测</a></li>
<li><a href="/2021/08/14/2021-%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%B3%B0%E4%BC%9A/">2021 暑期峰会</a></li>
</ol>
<h4 id="杂项"><a href="#杂项" class="headerlink" title="杂项"></a>杂项</h4><p>像个笑话一样的<a href="/2021/07/11/%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/">计划</a>。</p>
<p>以及稍微有些珍贵的，那些随笔的<a href="/2021/06/10/%E5%86%8C%E9%A1%B5/">册页</a>。</p>
]]></content>
